    dc:description "FIGURE 62. Eupelmus matranus, ♀. a–c (hоlоtуре): a, hеаd, frоntоlаtеrаl; b, right аntеnnа; c, dоrsаl hаbitus. d, mеsоsоmа, dоrsаl (2012-41). e, lаtеrаl hаbitus (2013-10). f, fоrе wing (2012-42)." ;
